cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CY, cs.SI 

This paper deals with natural language processing and machine learning, specifically focusing on word embeddings and bias mitigation strategies. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). It could also fall under cs.LG (Machine Learning), as it deals with training models and reducing invalid inferences. Additionally, it could be categorized under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) as it deals with improving the accuracy of AI models. The paper also discusses the impact of bias on the embeddings, which could fall under cs.CY (Computers and Society) or cs.SI (Social and Information Networks).
